messages.message: Hi @jack.robbins @Serena, just wanted to give a quick update for my run results api PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/73968), Anil left some comments which required some changes. Given that this is a public API this is something that we should try to make really clean and get right the first time, this may not be able to get in by eod today (I addressed his initial comments need to see if he adds anymore)

What about by tomorrow? If these changes are behind a feature flag and we could clean some of it up later, does that help reduce scope? Need to get something to MunichRe asap, so docs/other GA ready concerns could be delayed since this is only for one early customer

I think by tomorrow should be doable
Just need Anil to review asap
